com.yynie.myutils

类 Logger

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yynie.myutils.Logger

  • public class Logger
extends java.lang.Object
    An utility class used to print log strings on Android Devices.
    More powerful level controller provided. Easy to use.
    作者:
    Yan.Nie

    • 方法详细资料

      • get

        public static Logger get(java.lang.Class clazz,
                         Logger.Level level)
        Create a Logger instance for one Class in which scope you want to use Looger to print log messages with the class's simpleName as the tag.
        参数:
        clazz - The owner class.
        level - set to the Logger.Level which would be the lowest level control in this scope. Pls note that level lower than the global control will be ignored.

      • get

        public static Logger get(java.lang.String tag,
                         Logger.Level level)
        Create a Logger instance for a specified TAG.
        参数:
        tag - specify a tag
        level - set to the Logger.Level which would be the lowest level control for this instance. Pls note that level lower than the global control will be ignored.

      • getGlobalLevel

        public static Logger.Level getGlobalLevel()
        get currently global level
        返回:
        global level

      • setGlobalLevel

        public static boolean setGlobalLevel(Logger.Level level)
        set global level. It will take effect immediately.
        参数:
        level -

      • setGlobalLevel

        public static boolean setGlobalLevel(int levelValue)
        set global level with the Level's integer value. It will take effect immediately.
        参数:
        levelValue -
        返回:
        return false if levelValue is illegal. return true if success.
